title: Trade Tsunami: Landry, Talib Dealt & Free Agency Lunch Props
itunes:title: Trade Tsunami: Landry, Talib Dealt & Free Agency Lunch Props
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling & Marc Sessler- break from the newsroom to break down the latest from the Trade Tsunami. The heroes recap Jarvis Landry being traded to the Browns (3:30), the Broncos dealing Aquib Talib (8:00) and Seattle officially releases Richard Sherman (17:00). We take a look at the all-time sandwich props standings and make some new free agency lunch props (37:00).
